Frank, I&#39;m very, very sorry.  I didn&#39;t mean to be condescending, or rude, or anything negative at all; I was merely trying to acknowledge your beliefs, because this is your board, and I know from your posts that you don&#39;t subscribe to ghost stuff.  We each have our own beliefs and views on this, and I respect yours.

I would hope that, in future, if I say anything offending like this again, you would chalk it up to me not having any tact -- it would never be my intention to piss you off or make you uncomfortable on your own board.



